<i>noun</i>: 부음 [부ː음], 부고 [부ː고] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부음 [부ː음]</dt><br>
<dd>obituary; news of a person's death</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 죽은 것을 알리는 소식.</dd><br>
<dd>The news that informs people of a person's death.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부고 [부ː고]</dt><br>
<dd>obituary; notice of death</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 죽음과 장례식 등을 알리는 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A report that announces one's death and funeral.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>